[
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> <st data-num=\"05416\" class=\"\">Nathan</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>. When he <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> David,<n id=\"2\" /> Nathan<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> \u201cThere <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">were</st> <st data-num=\"08147\" class=\"\">two</st> <st data-num=\"0582\" class=\"\">men</st> in <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">a certain</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st>, <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"06223\" class=\"\">rich</st> and <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">the other</st> <st data-num=\"07326\" class=\"\">poor</st>. ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"06223\" class=\"\">rich man</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">had</st> a <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"07235\" class=\"\">many</st> <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">flocks</st> and <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">herds</st>. ",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "But the <st data-num=\"07326\" class=\"\">poor man</st> had <st data-num=\"0369 03605\">nothing</st> <st data-num=\"03588 0518\">except for</st> <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">a</st> <st data-num=\"06996\" class=\"\">little</st> <st data-num=\"03535 0834\">lamb</st> he had <st data-num=\"07069\" class=\"\">acquired</st>. He <st data-num=\"02421\" class=\"\">raised</st> it, and it <st data-num=\"01431\" class=\"\">grew up</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">alongside</st> him <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">and</st> his <st data-num=\"01121 03162\">children</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> It used to<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">eat</st> his <st data-num=\"06595\" class=\"\">food</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"08354\" class=\"\">drink</st> from his <st data-num=\"03563\" class=\"\">cup</st>, and <st data-num=\"07901\" class=\"\">sleep</st> in his <st data-num=\"02436\" class=\"\">arms</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> It <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> just like a <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughter</st> to him.</p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">\u201cWhen a <st data-num=\"01982\" class=\"\">traveler</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">arrived</st> at the <st data-num=\"06223\" class=\"\">rich</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man\u2019s</st> home,<n id=\"1\" /> he did <st data-num=\"02550\" class=\"\">not want</st> to <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">use</st> one of his own <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">sheep</st> or <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">cattle</st> to <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">feed</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"0732\" class=\"\">traveler</st> who had <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> to visit him.<n id=\"3\" /> Instead, he <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">took</st> the <st data-num=\"07326\" class=\"\">poor</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"03535\" class=\"\">lamb</st> and <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">cooked</st><n id=\"4\" /> it for the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> who had <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> visit him.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"0639 01732\">David</st> <st data-num=\"02734\" class=\"\">became</st> <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">very</st> <st data-num=\"02734\" class=\"\">angry</st> at this <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st>. He <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"05416\" class=\"\">Nathan</st>, \u201cAs surely as the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">lives</st>, the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> who <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">did</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"03588 01121\">deserves</st> to <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">die</st>!<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"06118 0834\">Because</st> he <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">committed</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"05921 0834 03808 02550\">cold-hearted</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">crime</st>, he must <st data-num=\"07999\" class=\"\">pay for</st> the <st data-num=\"03535\" class=\"\">lamb</st> <st data-num=\"0706\" class=\"\">four times over</st>!\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"05416\" class=\"\">Nathan</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st> are that <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st>! <st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> has <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>: <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">\u2018I</st> <st data-num=\"04886\" class=\"\">chose</st><n id=\"1\" /> you to be <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> and <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"05337\" class=\"\">rescued</st> you from the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> of <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>. ",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "I <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">gave</st> you your <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">master\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st>, and put your <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">master\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wives</st> into your <st data-num=\"02436\" class=\"\">arms</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> I also <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">gave</st> you the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> and <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>. And <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">if</st> all that somehow seems <st data-num=\"04592\" class=\"\">insignificant</st>, I would have <st data-num=\"03254\" class=\"\">given</st> you <st data-num=\"02007 02007\">so much more as well</st>!",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"04069\" class=\"\">Why</st> have you <st data-num=\"0959\" class=\"\">shown contempt</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">decrees</st><n id=\"1\" /> by <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">doing</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st> in my<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">sight</st>? You have <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">struck down</st> <st data-num=\"0223\" class=\"\">Uriah</st> the <st data-num=\"02850\" class=\"\">Hittite</st> with the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> and you have <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">taken</st> his <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wife</st> to be your own <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wife</st>! You have <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">killed</st> him with the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> of the <st data-num=\"01121 05983\">Ammonites</st>. ",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> will <st data-num=\"03808 05704 05769\">never</st> <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">depart</st> from your <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st>. <st data-num=\"06118 03588\">For</st> you have <st data-num=\"0959\" class=\"\">despised</st> me by <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">taking</st> the <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wife</st> of <st data-num=\"0223\" class=\"\">Uriah</st> the <st data-num=\"02850\" class=\"\">Hittite</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">as</st> your <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">own</st>!\u2019",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said:</st> \u2018I am <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">about</st> to <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">disaster</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> you<n id=\"1\" /> from inside your own <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">household</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> Right before your <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st> I will <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">take</st> your <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wives</st> and <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">hand</st> them <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">over</st> to your <st data-num=\"07453\" class=\"\">companion</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> He will <st data-num=\"07901\" class=\"\">go to bed</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st><n id=\"4\" /> your <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wives</st> in <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">broad</st> <st data-num=\"08121 02063\">daylight</st>!<n id=\"5\" />",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Although</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> have <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">acted</st> in <st data-num=\"05643\" class=\"\">secret</st>, <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">thing</st> <st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">before</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, and <st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">in broad</st> <st data-num=\"08121\" class=\"\">daylight</st>.\u2019\u201d<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">exclaimed</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"05416\" class=\"\">Nathan</st>, \u201cI have <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">sinned</st> against the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>!\u201d <st data-num=\"05416\" class=\"\">Nathan</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">Yes</st>, and the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">forgiven</st><n id=\"1\" /> your <st data-num=\"02403\" class=\"\">sin</st>. You are <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> going to <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">die</st>. ",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0657\" class=\"\">Nonetheless</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> you have <st data-num=\"05006\" class=\"\">treated</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05006\" class=\"\">with</st> <st data-num=\"05006\" class=\"\">such</st> <st data-num=\"05006\" class=\"\">contempt</st><n id=\"1\" /> in <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">matter</st>, the <st data-num=\"01571 01121\">son</st> who has been <st data-num=\"03209\" class=\"\">born</st> to you will <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">certainly</st> <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">die</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"05416\" class=\"\">Nathan</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">went</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> his <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">home</st>. The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05062\" class=\"\">struck</st> the <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"0223\" class=\"\">Uriah\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wife</st> had <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">borne</st> to <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, and the child <st data-num=\"0605\" class=\"\">became</st> very <st data-num=\"0605\" class=\"\">ill</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "Then <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"01245\">prayed to</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"01157\" class=\"\">for</st> the <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">child</st> and <st data-num=\"06684 01732 06685\">fasted</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> He would even<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">go</st> and <st data-num=\"03885\" class=\"\">spend the night</st> <st data-num=\"07901\" class=\"\">lying</st> on the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st>. ",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"02205\" class=\"\">elders</st> of his <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">stood</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> him and tried to <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">lift</st> him <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st>, but he was <st data-num=\"03808 014\">unwilling</st>, and <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">refused</st> to <st data-num=\"01254\" class=\"\">eat</st> <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> them.</p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">On the <st data-num=\"01961 07637\">seventh</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> the <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">died</st>. But the <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st> of <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">were afraid</st> to <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">inform</st> him <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> the <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> had <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">died</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> they <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">While</st> the <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> still <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">alive</st> he would <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listen</st> to <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">us</st><n id=\"1\" /> when we <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">spoke</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> him. <st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">How</st> can we <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">tell</st> him that the <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">is dead</st>? He will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st> himself <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">harm</st>!\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> his <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st> were <st data-num=\"03907\" class=\"\">whispering to one another</st>, <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">he</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">realized</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> the <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">was dead</st>. So <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">asked</st> his <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">Is</st> the <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">dead</st>?\u201d They <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cYes, he<st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">\u2019s dead</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">got up</st> from the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st>, <st data-num=\"07364\" class=\"\">bathed</st>, <st data-num=\"05480\" class=\"\">put on oil</st>, and <st data-num=\"02498\" class=\"\">changed</st> his <st data-num=\"08071\" class=\"\">clothes</st>. He <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">went</st> to the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> and <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">worshiped</st>. Then, when he <st data-num=\"0935 0413\">entered</st> his <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">palace</st>, he <st data-num=\"07592\" class=\"\">requested</st> that <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st> be <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">brought</st> to him, and he <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">ate</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">His <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> him, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> is <st data-num=\"01697 02088\">this</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> you have <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st>? <st data-num=\"05668\" class=\"\">While</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> was still <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">alive</st>, you <st data-num=\"06684\" class=\"\">fasted</st> and <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">wept</st>. <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">Once</st> the <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">was dead</st> you <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">got up</st> and <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">ate</st> <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st>!\u201d ",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cWhile the <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> was <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">still</st> <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">alive</st>, I <st data-num=\"06684\" class=\"\">fasted</st> and <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">wept</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">thought</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u2018<st data-num=\"04310 03045\">Perhaps</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> will <st data-num=\"02603\" class=\"\">show pity</st> and the <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> will <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">live</st>.\u2019 ",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "But <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> he <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">is dead</st>. <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">should</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"06684\" class=\"\">fast</st>? <st data-num=\"03201\" class=\"\">Am</st> I <st data-num=\"03201\" class=\"\">able</st> to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">bring</st> him <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">back</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">at this point</st>? <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> him, but <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">cannot</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">return</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">comforted</st> his <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wife</st> <st data-num=\"01339\" class=\"\">Bathsheba</st>. He <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> her<n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"07901\" class=\"\">went to bed</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> her.<n id=\"2\" /> Later she <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">gave birth to</st> a <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>, and David<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"07121 08034\">named</st> him <st data-num=\"08010\" class=\"\">Solomon</st>. Now the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0157\" class=\"\">loved</st> the child<n id=\"4\" />",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "and <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> word <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">through</st> <st data-num=\"05416\" class=\"\">Nathan</st> the <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophet</st> that he should be <st data-num=\"07121 08034\">named</st> <st data-num=\"03041\" class=\"\">Jedidiah</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05668\" class=\"\">for</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"05668\" class=\"\">sake</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><n id=\"1\" /> So <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"03898\" class=\"\">fought</st> against <st data-num=\"07237\" class=\"\">Rabbah</st> of the <st data-num=\"01121 05983\">Ammonites</st> and <st data-num=\"03920\" class=\"\">captured</st> the <st data-num=\"04410\" class=\"\">royal</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st>. ",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> then <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">messengers</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st>, \u201cI have <st data-num=\"03898\" class=\"\">fought</st> against <st data-num=\"07237\" class=\"\">Rabbah</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">and</st> have <st data-num=\"03920\" class=\"\">captured</st> the <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water supply</st> of the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">assemble</st> the <st data-num=\"03499\" class=\"\">rest</st> of the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"02583 05921\">besiege</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> and <st data-num=\"03920\" class=\"\">capture</st> it. <st data-num=\"06435\" class=\"\">Otherwise</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"03920\" class=\"\">capture</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> and it will be <st data-num=\"07121 08034\">named</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">for</st> me.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">assembled</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> and <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">went</st> to <st data-num=\"07237\" class=\"\">Rabbah</st> and <st data-num=\"03898\" class=\"\">fought</st> against it and <st data-num=\"03920\" class=\"\">captured</st> it.",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">took</st> the <st data-num=\"05850\" class=\"\">crown</st> of their <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">from</st> his <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st>\u2014it was <st data-num=\"02091\" class=\"\">gold</st>, <st data-num=\"04948\" class=\"\">weighed</st> <st data-num=\"03603\" class=\"\">about 75 pounds</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> and held a <st data-num=\"03368\" class=\"\">precious</st> <st data-num=\"068\" class=\"\">stone</st>\u2014and it <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> placed <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st>. He also <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">took from</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> a <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"07235\" class=\"\">deal</st> of <st data-num=\"07998\" class=\"\">plunder</st>. ",
    "verse": "30"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "12",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">removed</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> were in it and <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">made</st> them labor with <st data-num=\"04050\" class=\"\">saws</st>, <st data-num=\"01270\" class=\"\">iron</st> <st data-num=\"02757\" class=\"\">picks</st>, and <st data-num=\"01270\" class=\"\">iron</st> <st data-num=\"04037\" class=\"\">axes</st>, <st data-num=\"05647\">putting</st> them <st data-num=\"05647\">to work</st><n id=\"2\" /> at the <st data-num=\"04404\" class=\"\">brick kiln</st>. <st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">This</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">was</st> his <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">policy</st><n id=\"3\" /> with <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 05983\">Ammonite</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st>. Then <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">returned</st> to <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "31"
  }
]